                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Varius <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audia</ex></expan> Sabinus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Sav</abbr><ex>aria</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>eneficiarius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>st</abbr><ex>ipendiorum</ex></expan> XVII <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXXV <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>ues</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>XV <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex cert="low">ecundus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> ex <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Surus
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nach Scherrer sehr wahrscheinlich eine moderne &amp;lt;span style=&amp;apos;color:red&amp;apos;&amp;gt;Fälschung&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Z. 8: auf der rechten Nebenseite; Schreibtechnik: eingeritzt. (B): AE 1992: Z. 1: Q. f.</p>
            </div>
